# Packages whose shared libraries / files the Blueberry base image already ships.
# A dep named here is treated as satisfied and is NOT installed, so packages
# don't try to reinstall what the base already provides. One name per line;
# #comments and blanks ignored. The built-in list in bpm's is_provided() (glibc,
# gcc-libs, bash, coreutils, ...) is EXTENDED by this file.
#
# Only list things actually present. The base bundles the glibc runtime plus:
#   libz.so.1      -> zlib
#   libzstd.so.1   -> zstd
#   liblzma.so.5   -> xz
#   liblz4.so.1    -> lz4
# and ships the CA bundle at /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt -> ca-certificates.
zlib
zstd
xz
lz4
ca-certificates
